<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā lalṣãbāḥi ạl̊mun̊taẓar̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ yaq̊dimu ạlrãbũ ạl̊majīd̊
 hunāka naḥ̊ẓay̱ biạlẓãfar̊
 wāl̊ḥam̊da nuh̊dī wālnãsẖīd̊

[V2]
 2- nasẖ̊dū ḥubūraⁿạ naf̊takẖir̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ ạảk̊mala ạlrãbũ ạl̊ʿuhūd̊
 nuh̊dī lahu ạl̊ḥam̊da ạl̊ʿaṭir̊
 nusabĩḥu dẖāka ạl̊wadūd̊

[V3]
 3- rā̊̉su ạl̊mulūki ạl̊mun̊taṣir
 nus̊dī lahu kulã ạlsũjūd̊
 waṣaẘlajānu ạl̊muq̊tadir̊
 baẙna ạl̊waray̱ yaq̊ḍī yasūd̊

[V4]
 4- biạs̊mihi llậbi ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 yaj̊tẖū ạl̊jamīʿu biạl̊waraʿ̊
 wakulã sẖaẙʾiⁿ ʿan̊ qarīb̊
 taḥ̊ta qadamaẙhi yaḍaʿ̊

[V5]
 5- yā ạảyũhā ạl̊fādī ạl̊muqīm̊
 ʿah̊da ạl̊fiday̱ fīmā ṣanaʿ̊
 nuh̊dī laka ạl̊ḥam̊da ạlrãkẖīm̊
 yā man̊ ʿalay̱ ạl̊kulĩ ạr̊tafaʿ̊</lyrics>
<title>yạ llṣbạḥ ạlmntẓr</title>
</song>